 situation?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Regarding the previous question, which of the following options best describes this situation?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Clear shared norm"},"2":{"Display":"Weak or unclear norm"},"3":{"Display":"Two competing norms"},"4":{"Display":"No clear norm"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2,3,4],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":5,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID93"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6tZ9inq7UmTQyHk","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID94","SecondaryAttribute":"Regarding the previous question","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Regarding the previous question","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionType":"Slider","Selector":"HSLIDER","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","CSSliderMin":0,"CSSliderMax":100,"GridLines":1,"SnapToGrid":false,"NumDecimals":"0","ShowValue":true,"CustomStart":false,"NotApplicable":false,"MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"Regarding the previous question","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"How much agreement do you think exists among people about what is appropriate in this situation?"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":2,"NextAnswerId":1,"Labels":[],"QuestionID":"QID94"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6tZ9inq7UmTQyHk","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID95","SecondaryAttribute":"Regarding the previous question, which of the following options best describes this situation?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Regarding the previous question, which of the following options best describes this situation?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Regarding the previous question, which of the following options best describes this situation?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Clear shared norm"},"2":{"Display":"Weak or unclear norm"},"3":{"Display":"Two competing norms"},"4":{"Display":"No clear norm"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2,3,4],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":5,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID95"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6tZ9inq7UmTQyHk","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID96","SecondaryAttribute":"In the next task, you will make a real decision involving a bonus payment. You will receive a $1....","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In the next task, you will make a real decision involving a bonus payment.\r\n\r\nYou will receive a $1.00 bonus for completing this study. You will be randomly paired with another participant in this study.\r\n\r\nYou will be assigned the role of Player A. The other participant will be Player B.\r\n\r\nAs Player A, you must decide how to divide the $1.00 bonus between yourself and Player B.\r\n\r\nYou may give any amount of the $1.00 to Player B. The amount you give will be transferred to them, and you will keep the remainder. For example<br>\u2022 If you give $0.00, you keep the entire $1.00, and Player B receives nothing.<br>\u2022 If you give $0.50, both you and Player B receive $0.50.<br>\u2022 If you give $1.00, Player B receives the entire $1.00, and you receive nothing.<br>Player B has no choice and must accept the allocation.\r\n\r\nYour decision will remain anonymous.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Behavior Task","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In the next task, you will make a real decision involving a bonus payment. You will receive a $1....","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID96"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6tZ9inq7UmTQyHk","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID97","SecondaryAttribute":"How much of the $ 1 bonus would you like to give to Player B?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"How much of the $ 1 bonus would you like to give to Player B?","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function() {\n    var q = jQuery(\"#\" + this.questionId);\n\n    \/\/ Hide handle initially\n    q.find(\".handle\").css('visibility', 'hidden');\n\n    \/\/ Show handle when user interacts\n    q.find(\".track\").on(\"click touchstart\", function() {\n        jQuery(this).find(\".handle\").css('visibility', 'visible');\n    });\n\n    \/\/ Make track thinner (optional UI)\n    q.find(\".track\").css(\"height\", \"10px\");\n});\n\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function() {\n    var q = this;\n\n    \/\/ Continuous snapping\n    var interval = setInterval(function() {\n        var val = q.getChoiceValue(1);\n\n        if (val !== null && val !== \"\") {\n            var snapped = Math.round(val \/ 10) * 10;\n\n            if (val != snapped) {\n                q.setChoiceValue(1, snapped);\n            }\n        }\n    }, 100);\n\n    \/\/ Stop interval when leaving page\n    this.addOnUnload(function() {\n        clearInterval(interval);\n    });\n});","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionID":"QID97","QuestionType":"Slider","Selector":"HSLIDER","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","CSSliderMin":0,"CSSliderMax":100,"GridLines":10,"SnapToGrid":false,"NumDecimals":"0","ShowValue":true,"CustomStart":false,"NotApplicable":false,"MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"How much of the $ 1 bonus would you like to give to Player B?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Your choice"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":2,"NextAnswerId":6,"Labels":{"1":{"Display":"0.00 (Give $0.00 to Player B; keep $1.00)"},"2":{"Display":"1.00  (Give $1.00 to Player B; keep $0.00)"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6tZ9inq7UmTQyHk","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID98","SecondaryAttribute":"If you choose to give $0.30 to Player B, how much money will you keep?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"If you choose to give $0.30 to Player B, how much money will you keep?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"If you choose to give $0.30 to Player B, how much money will you keep?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"0.30"},"2":{"Display":"0.50"},"3":{"Display":"0.70"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID98"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6tZ9inq7UmTQyHk","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID99","SecondaryAttribute":"In the following section, you will read several short scenarios. For each scenario, you will eval...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In the following section, you will read several short scenarios.\n<br>For each scenario, you will evaluate different possible actions and rate how socially appropriate each action is.\n\nPlease answer carefully. <br>Your responses may influence whether you receive a bonus for matching the most common response among participants.","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In the following section, you will read several short scenarios. For each scenario, you will eval...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"In the following section, you will read several short scenarios.\n<br>For each scenario, you will evaluate different possible actions and rate how socially appropriate each action is.\n\nPlease answer carefully. <br>Your responses may influence whether you receive a bonus for matching the most common response among participants.","DataExportTag":"","QuestionID":"QID99"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6tZ9inq7UmTQyHk","Element":"STAT","PrimaryAttribute":"Survey Statistics","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"MobileCompatible":true,"ID":"Survey Statistics"}}]}